---
import BaseLayout from '../layout/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
  <h1>Releases - R10Progress</h1>
  <section id="releases">
    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3>Version 1.0.0</h3>
        <p>
          Initial release of R10Progress. Track your progress and goals with the
          Garmin Approach R10 Golf Radar.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Version 1.1.0</h3>
        <p>
          Added the ability to compare your current session to your previous
          sessions. Choose freely what data and club you want to see.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Version 1.2.0</h3>
        <p>
          Added the ability to remove outliers using IQR filtering or just focus
          on the above average shots in the Shot Dispersion graph.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Version 1.3.0</h3>
        <p>
          Added the ability to compare the relationship between two data points
          in the Shot Scatter Plot. For example, you can compare the relationship
          between your club speed and shot distance or maybe your club path and
          the sidespin or deviation distance!
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3>Version 1.3.1</h3>
        <p>
          Improved a lot of the mobile experience. The app is now more responsive.
          We also offer the app as a PWA (Progressive Web App) so you can install
          it on your phone and use it offline.
        </p>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
